videos.description: Manahattan's Ahmed Ismail gets rejected going to the rim by Monmouth's Je'lon Hornbeak. In transition, Hornbeak dribbles into the paint looking for layup of his own, but gets blocks by Ismail.
videos.headline: Manhattan's Ismail gets block revenge
